description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on streamer, Cizzorz. They discuss their predictions for the Fortnite World Cup, storming Area 51, Cizzorz's Deathrun maps, and more!
